    "For all settings, we clip the gradient norm to 5.0.",
    "Typical data augmentations including random width/height shift and horizontal flip are applied.For WebVision dataset, we follow the experimental setting in previous works [42].",
    "We train a ResNet-50 [3] using SGD for 250 epochs with initial learning rate 0.4, nesterov momentum 0.9 and weight decay 3 × 10 -5 (for our proposed ANL methods, the weight decay is set to 0) and batch size 512.",
    "The learning rate is multiplied by 0.97 after every epoch of training.",
    "For all settings, we clip the gradient norm to 5.0."
  ],
